      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ablility to define, interpret and enforce government legislation and policy</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Citizen Management</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ablility to identify a citizen, maintain information on them and the status of their interactions and agreements</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Businss Organisation Management</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ablility to identify a business organisation (school, business, etc), maintain information on them and the status of their interactions and agreements</td>
    </tr>
