      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Authorisations Management</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ablility to define and manage process that enables the provision of rights/entitlements (financial or otherwise) to people and/or assets</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Public Awareness</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ability to disseminate information that is useful, important or beneficial to the public and to respond to queries</td>
    </tr>  
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Asset Management</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ability to acquire, create, track, report on, maintain and dispose of, tangible or intangible assets, with intrinsic value</td>
    </tr>      
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Operations Management   </th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ablility to manage a workforce, processes and information in order to support the provision of NICS services</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Procurement Management</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ablility to develop and maintain the procurement of assets, products and services on behalf of NICS</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">ICT Management</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ablility to provide and manage ICT services both to staff and citizens</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Facilities Management</th>
      <td class="govuk-table__cell">The ablility to procure and maintain facilities required by staff in accordance with Health & Safety laws</td>
    </tr>
    <tr class="govuk-table__row">
      <th scope="row" class="govuk-table__header">Financial Management</th>
